gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Big gathering built by chief, Saint went to Surat city; 
Very renounced wealth threefold, Knowledgeable one devotedly worshiped many.

Here is the translation:

God makes love stories happen, and then You surrender Yourself to Him; 
Show me the path of salvation now, and distinguish truth from falsehood.

Blue sky got covered, this way trouble came to pass.
Grief stricken, saintly play occurred; 

The rope was tied around the throat, crying stopped working, hope of rising did not remain.
